title: 'My life is in danger': Irish boy trapped in Gaza desperate to get home
description: A young boy from Ireland who became trapped in Gaza after Israel began its retaliatory strikes against Hamas has said he is desperate to get home.

title: Hamas terrorists were carrying instructions on how to make chemical weapons, Israeli president claims
description: Hamas terrorists who broke into Israel were carrying instructions on how to make chemical weapons, according to Israeli President Isaac Herzog.

title: Family of missing UK teenager say she was murdered in Hamas attack on Israel
description: A 16-year-old British girl reported missing after the Hamas attack on Israel was murdered by the militant group, her family have said.

title: This perilous conflict could erupt into war with global impact - one not even the US could stop
description: With tensions in the Middle East at boiling point after Hamas triggered a war with Israel, there are growing risks of uncontrolled escalation - plunging the whole region into conflict.

title: Chainsaw-wielding TikTok economic takes the lead in first round of Argentina election
description: Argentines are heading to the polls as a chainsaw-wielding TikTok economist took the lead in the first round of voting.

title: Iranian journalists jailed over coverage of protests sparked by Mahsa Amini death
description: Two journalists have been jailed for their coverage of protests sparked by the death of a woman in Iran last year, Iranian state media has reported.

title: Palestinian ambassador blames Gaza hospital blast on Israel
description: The Palestinian ambassador to the UK has claimed Israel was responsible for a hospital blast in Gaza that killed hundreds.

title: Teenage girl 'left brain dead' after being 'attacked for not wearing a hijab'
description: A teenage girl allegedly attacked by Iranian authorities for not wearing a hijab is said to be "brain dead", state media in the country has reported.

title: Vinicius Junior praises Sevilla for ejecting 'racist fan'
description: Real Madrid footballer Vinicius Junior has praised Sevilla for its swift actions in ejecting a supporter who allegedly racially abused him during a La Liga match.

title: More than 50 Palestinians reported killed in overnight airstrikes on Gaza - as Israel targets mosque in West Bank
description: Five people have been killed in the West Bank as Israel carried out a strike on a mosque it says was used to organise attacks -  as more than 50 Palestinians are reported to have died in rocket attacks on Gaza overnight.

title: Six killed in 'Russian missile' attack on postal centre in Kharkiv
description: Six people have been killed and at least 14 injured in a Russian missile attack that hit a postal distribution centre in Kharkiv, Ukrainian officials have said.
